videos.headline: Boston, Cooke serve up comeback win for No. 1 Gamecocks
videos.description: Aliyah Boston and Zia Cooke combine for 41 points on 17-for-25 field-goal shooting as South Carolina closes on a 45-18 run in a 95-66 win at Kentucky.
